00:08:24,950 --> 00:08:26,330
Cuánto tiempo sin vernos, Satoru.

128
00:08:26,330 --> 00:08:28,040
Te ves bien, Satoru.

129
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,080
Kobayashi Kenya y Sugita Hiromi

130
00:08:32,330 --> 00:08:34,960
eran dos de mis mejores amigos.

131
00:08:35,290 --> 00:08:38,000
Kenya ahora es un abogado,
y Hiromi un doctor.

132
00:08:39,460 --> 00:08:41,840
Hablamos de cosas sin sentido.

133
00:08:43,180 --> 00:08:46,140
